<article class="row hentry post-258525 to4_article_post type-to4_article_post status-publish has-post-thumbnail category-interview tag-donald-trump tag-immigrants tag-jobs tag-noam-chomsky tag-tariffs tag-tax-cut tag-trade-war tag-unemployment section-politics-and-elections primary_topic-politics" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ReportageNewsArticle">
