<div class="">
<h2 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">
<a href="https://truthout.org/articles/the-trump-economy-myth-and-job-killing-policies/">The Trump Economy Myth and Job-Killing Policies</a>
</h2>
</div>
<div class="entry-summary" itemprop="description">
<div>
<div class="entry-summary">Propaganda is one thing, but Trump&#8217;s actual policies will hurt job and wage growth once they kick in.</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="entry-meta">
<dl class="article__authors byline">
<dt class="meta-label">by </dt>
<dd class="author vcard" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name"><a class="url fn" href="https://truthout.org/authors/dave-johnson/" itemprop="url" rel="author">Dave Johnson</a></span>, </dd>
<dd class="source org" itemprop="sourceOrganization" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Organization"><span itemprop="name"><a href='https://ourfuture.org/20170410/the-trump-economy-myth' itemprop='url'>Campaign for America's Future</a></span></dd>
</dl>
